AttributeList.Text: ============================================================================= This module is used in Applications when a roller two way two Speed equipped with contactor is needed. The roller can support single body tranport and simultanious transport. The roller is equiped with a standard sensor setting (two at the rear and two at the front for high/low Speed transport). The roller shall use standard handshaking signals to accomplish an infeed transfer with the previous transport system and an outfeed with the next transport system (in both directions). The roller will support automatic Mode and manual Mode according specific guidelines. All transport rollers shall use the same principle techniques. The outfeed will be master over the infeed Alarm "body not in Position" is also generated. All Alarms coming from sub-functions (TrfIn, TrfOut & Motor2W2S-C) or from local Alarm (see above) are summarized to give also the global Alarm A, B, C & D to upper level. =============================================================================
